	<h1 class="title">一个染发师谈论她工作的艺术，关于色彩心理学</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/121376/small/121376.jpg?1434268095" alt="">
